Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:10.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:19.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Jinnai Tomonori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:28.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you all remember the suspicious person who appeared in the "live broadcast"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:34.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I do  \N-That was fun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:37.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For this supposed live broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:41.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yoshimura did very well
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:45.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,His popularity rose \N-He was on network news
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:47.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yoshimura received great acclaim
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This revealed that experience helps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:54.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As Abareru and Ogata both got into a little panic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:58.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Maybe they didn't perform well because they're not senior enough \N-That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:01.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, this time, i've brought the following theory
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:08.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If a suspicious person interrupts a live broadcast, an experienced announcer can handle it perfectly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:11.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see. How will veterans deal with it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:17.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After this, veteran announcer vs. suspicious passersby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:18.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:19.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I got married at the age of 16
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:23.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Another collection of families with a small age gap
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 2nd 4 Generation Relay Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:32.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then, when getting hit by a colorless stinky air cannon while being criticized
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:33.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You won't mention the stench
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:58.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If a suspicious person interrupts a live broadcast, an experienced announcer can handle it perfectly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of people will do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:02:00.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's see who it is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:05.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time we set up a supposed live broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:10.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And invited experienced craftsmen with more than 30 years of experience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:16.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To cover a BBQ venue in Saitama for a fictional program
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems legitimate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:21.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,During the live broadcast, the suspicious passerby will pay a visit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:28.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course, this time, the actor who was previously well-received for his role as a suspicious character, is back again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:36.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the case. The first target is Akihiro Yoshimura, 44th year of the Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:37.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You got a great guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:45.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yoshimura has been on air every week for ten years
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:45.54,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※A long-running Japanese variety show broadcast on TBS from 11:45 to 12:54 every Sunday since October 6, 1985
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.54,0:02:46.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How will he handle the situation?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The live broadcast begins
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.02,0:02:57.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time we have Mr. Akihiro Yoshimura, come on out, Mr. Yoshimura~
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.50,0:03:02.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Akihiro Yoshimura!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really nice to have a BBQ in spring
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:14.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So today, we came to the BBQ site in Saitama, Arima Gorge
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:16.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Feels stable
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:18.66,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's worthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:21.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point in the broadcast, we get the guy out as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:25.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In this new green period of the coming summer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:27.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,BBQ in spring like this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:32.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It may not have much to do with summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:35.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:38.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're live right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Brother. Brother. \N -Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:44.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So today we come to interview people who are interested in fishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:48.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To interview rainbow trout fishermen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:51.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Brother, what are you doing here...are you here to fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:52.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Brother, brother, are you fishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you come to fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fishing, fishing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Brother... brother let's fish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:01.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Brother, let's fish, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:05.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With the sudden intrusion, although there is a moment of timidity
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:10.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He quickly recovers and continues the live coverage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:11.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:16.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are still a lot of fishermen, let's turn back a little to see
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is a foot bath
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:24.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because there are very few people today, you can soak your feet for a little rest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:26.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Look this way next
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:29.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Great, great, too impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:30.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:36.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There may be those who come fishing without their equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:39.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are also BBQ sets full sets can be rented
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:45.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The cost of a set (half day) is 2500 yen and 3700 yen a day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:48.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,People with no rod and bait can also come here to rent
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:51.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In such a way, he throws the topic to distant building facilities
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:56.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To cleverly lead the camera to the place where the crazy guy isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:05:00.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A skill that only veterans possess
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Worthy of a veteran
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:05.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, as usual, after properly handling this pestering guy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:09.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then we will introduce you to the BBQ venue afterwards
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll take you back to the studio for now.  \N-Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:14.35,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Easy to get around him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:18.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Reducing the impact to a minimum with this wonderful performance, the camera goes back to the studio
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:24.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that, he continued to report cheerfully without showing any sense of surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:29.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a staff problem  \N-The staff should have gone to stop it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:34.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next step is to escalate the crazy level
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What exactly will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are young people fishing here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're taking a break for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you guys have any fishing experience in the sea, river or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No. \N -No?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:50.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But most people would have been to the fishing pond, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:54.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I haven't been there either. \N -It's also not common anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:06:01.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, brother, brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are rainbow trout here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're not a zombie either, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:16.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Brother, move slightly to the side... just stay there for a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:24.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From the river, a wet zombie appears and its still greeted with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:27.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So here we reveal the project
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:32.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,May I ask what program you thought you were invited to today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:35.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh... Uncle Broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:39.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's actually Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:44.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's why a guy like that came? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:48.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You guys are skilled
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Terrific
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even went in the water
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:53.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's so cold
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next target is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:00.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,32 years experience, Kikuhime Hayashiya
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:00.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Same as my rakugo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:01.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,She's a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:09.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kikuhime who was active as an announcer on TBS's information program "Just" in the first half of the 2000s
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:09.70,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※"Just" was broadcast live on TBS Life from September 28, 1998 to March 25, 2005 in the afternoon on weekdays
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's get started
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:10.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A woman
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.19,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Could be a little scared
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the lake called Lake Naguri
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:18.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It may sound shocking to hear the name of autumn chestnut
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:21.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? Hello, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Would you like to present for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:26.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's very sudden but sorry. Are you here to play too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:30.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You are also here, it's a little... sorry... so suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:34.41,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hasn't changed her face yet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:35.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then around here, there's also boating in this lake
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:38.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are also places to fish
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:42.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In autumn, you can also enjoy the beautiful maple leaves here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a great place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So let's take a look at this side again
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There seems to be a visitor who is having a good time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:53.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For the sudden arrival of the crazy guy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This one also continues without the slightest panic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:00.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How many people came together today? \N -5 people or so
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:04.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you fish often?\N-My supervisor is more...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is your boss. \N -Yes, for now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:10.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you fish often?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:14.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are no opportunities after work
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wow, wet, why are you wet this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:23.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, that... Why are you wet this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:28.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to be catching much fish here, so I'll come back when you get some
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:33.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Some uneasiness is felt about the river appearence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:34.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:39.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's okay, because the climate is great. It's very pleasant
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:43.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Being able to do it under the blue sky is also one of the joys of BBQ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:45.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From my perspective as an older woman, I like it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:47.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's cool and you don't sweat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All equipment can be rented here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:53.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I like it, so I suggest you try it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:55.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surely an instinctive reaction would manifest slightly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:09:00.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ultimately, she ends up in a scary situation live
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:03.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We are actually Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My favorite show!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:18.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Despite saying this, she failed to realise
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of theory do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.41,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's your favorite program, after all
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:26.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Joints and such? Eh what what what? Joints?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:27.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What joints?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:31.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That... the knee joint
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:30.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:32.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You don't even know this show, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Definitely doesn't know the program
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bone joint?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:39.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Regardless of whether they're funny or not, veteran broadcasters are undoubtedly skilled like the theory suggests
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:41.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't say stuff like "regardless of whether they're funny or not"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:43.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hi~ I'm Nakamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Known as TVchampion's former announcer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:51.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yuki Nakamura with 45 years of experience
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:51.87,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※TVchampion was a variety show broadcast on TV Tokyo every Thursday from 19:30 to 20:50 from April 16, 1992 to September 21, 2006
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:54.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Today we came to Arima Valley
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:59.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It takes about an hour and a half to get here by car from Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That...can...can reach
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:05.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Possibly because he hasn't been on TV for too long
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:08.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nakamura stumbles even without obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:08.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't say such things
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we get things moving
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:12.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The maple leaves in autumn are really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:16.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The tourists coming for a walk also... should be a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, wait a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:23.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We... we're on the air now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where did you come from today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:27.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:35.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is obvious that the unexpected appearance of unexpected and suspicious people is a surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rainbow trout can be caught here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you going to follow me all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:49.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because we are live a lot of things will happen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:52.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, this customer seems to be particularly fond of the camera
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:57.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please go to the side... just a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:02.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a completely incoherent
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:08.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The river appearance is also a mess
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:16.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:19.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Always in a state of handicap, the broadcast ends
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:23.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that the fourth target is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:28.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chin with 33 years of experience
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A veteran broadcaster who is known for his door-to-door visits to outside locations
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:37.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How will he deal with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:41.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can also see maple leaves here in autumn
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:44.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a great place to get away from it all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:50.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So today, sir, sorry, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Today ah, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:55.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sir, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No problem? \N -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:59.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir, what's wrong with you? I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:06.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Today, let's see how happy the spring BBQ is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I would like to introduce you to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but we're shooting now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:14.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Treating suspicious people with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:18.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chin, who speaks to others while looking them in the eye
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But after that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sir, I know, what is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:28.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here? What's going on? Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:35.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Busy with the crazy guy, the broadcast is neglected
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this moment the broadcast goes back to the studio
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:43.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To let the staff intervene to get rid of the crazy guy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:45.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sir, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:51.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on? What's wrong? It's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.36,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very kind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't be  too rough with him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:57.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A nice guy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:13:02.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chin, more concerned about the man than the flow of the broadcast, is thrown off slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:06.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can tell that this is a kind person...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:11.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's great to catch two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For newbies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:20.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:21.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on? What on earthl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:25.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Come on up! Let's get you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:34.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:39.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That towel, towel towel towel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:42.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's too nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, you were shocked, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:47.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was shocked too
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Alongside helping the crazy guy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:53.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He also doesn't forget the subject of the interview
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:58.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Aside from being a broadcaster, he is an excellent human being
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:02.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really comfortable to be in nature
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:04.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed, you will also want to jump into the water
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:07.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because it's comfortable. It's comfortable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:10.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'll want to jump in... don't jump is fine too
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's okay not to dive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This kid is so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:24.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In a state where even Chin can't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We reveal the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Afterwards
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:31.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That person is from Wednesday Downtown?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:32.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.05,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is a well-mannered person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:35.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I wanna cry
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:41.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was also moved to tears because you are so gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:45.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, that's great
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:48.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:52.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An unexpected and heart-warming scene
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:56.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The final target is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:02.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The oldest, 79-year-old Eiji Bando
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,...apologizing just now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:08.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry for wearing the Lions hat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That kind of thing is fine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:10.16,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※The Lions refer to the Saitama Seibu Lions, a team in the Pacific League of Nippon Professional Baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did something happen? \N -Sorry, a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:21.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?  \N-That's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:24.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because it is a live broadcast, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:28.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although this part has unfolded similarly so far
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:29.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It feels like something bad is going to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:31.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Raise it a little. Raise it a little
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's good to shoot here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:37.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Caught! Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:41.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You guys keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:44.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:45.40,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pushed away
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.64,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Slightly pushed away
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:48.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because it's live
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just pushed him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:55.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,BBQ is fully available here, and is waiting for your reservation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pushed away hard
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:03.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The forced removal of a suspicious person causing trouble constantly
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:05.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tough to shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:05.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:07.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As we need to prepare a little now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:13.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the studio please \N -Okay thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:16.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Later, we will introduce more beautiful places, please look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Broadcast back to the studio
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Damn, I'm scared
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can this be broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is something that can't be broadcast, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:32.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just watch for the time being
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:40.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0201FB&\3c&HFFFFFF&}In summary \N{\c\3c}It seems like some parts of this wont make it to broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:42.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:48.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking the whole of the last part will have to be cut
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:55.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's some discussions going on about compliance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:58.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto, what do you think?\N  -About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please comment on Bando's part first
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:07.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it was spiritually invigorating
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:08.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It won't be forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:15.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We've once again witnessed the spirit of Showa-era men that had been forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:18.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They have to find a way to make the show work
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:22.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bando was the only one to not interact with the guy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:25.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because he thought he was trying to cause trouble on purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He was pretty cool
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:31.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How about we just don't say the name "Bando" in the clip
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everyone will still know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:37.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just write "Some Old Man"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Or refer to him as just A
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was a shocking sight wasn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:48.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you do this to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:51.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The voice is so obviously his!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I feel like covering the eyes will work
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:59.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And make the name A or B or something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So everyone please look forward to the eventual broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm scared it'll get cut
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:12.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah but this show is so stupid
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.02,0:18:16.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome the next presenter
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.48,0:18:21.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone
Dialogue: 2,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Shimofuri!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:26.14,0:18:27.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.76,0:18:34.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, we are not bringing a theory but a project
Dialogue: 2,0:18:34.16,0:18:36.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?  \N-Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hope its something heart-warming
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.81,0:18:38.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,True
Dialogue: 2,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hope this next segment will be aired in its entirety
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.26,0:18:41.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It should be
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.25,0:18:44.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please offset the bad vibes
Dialogue: 2,0:18:44.29,0:18:45.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What we have brought is this:
Dialogue: 2,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 2nd 4 Generation Relay Competition
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah
Dialogue: 2,0:18:51.01,0:19:00.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Previously we had a children Mothers Grandmothers and Great-grandmothers relay race
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.19,0:19:05.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How about this, the family aspect is heart-warming, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, warm
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just a little relay race...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:10.10,0:19:11.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with the relay race, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:11.41,0:19:14.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. Relay is also very good
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are relay races really heartwarming?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It can be a chance for family bonding
Dialogue: 2,0:19:17.40,0:19:20.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can just a little bit of heartwarming content fill the hole we have now?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, the last part was a bit much
