Dialogue: 2,0:25:23.87,0:25:28.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was told "Your mom is super cute" the other day
Dialogue: 2,0:25:28.81,0:25:31.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the second son Keiji
Dialogue: 2,0:25:31.64,0:25:34.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the third son Taizan
Dialogue: 2,0:25:34.68,0:25:39.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fourth child and fifth child
Dialogue: 2,0:25:40.53,0:25:43.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A mother with a lot of children
Dialogue: 2,0:25:44.32,0:25:47.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's my first husband's child
Dialogue: 2,0:25:47.52,0:25:51.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The rest are my current husband's
Dialogue: 2,0:25:52.16,0:25:57.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Divorced three years after giving birth to the eldest son at the age of 19
Dialogue: 2,0:25:58.64,0:26:04.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,2 years later, she remarried her current husband, Masao
Dialogue: 2,0:26:05.88,0:26:09.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And they had four children
Dialogue: 2,0:26:12.25,0:26:15.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Masao's children start with the second child
